[[File:משפריצות פעולה ורודה 2.jpg|thumb|[[Anarcho-queer]] collective Mashpritzot hold a [[die-in]] protest against Israeli pinkwashing and the perceived [[homonormativity|homo-normative]] priorities of the [[LGBTQ]] support centre in [[Tel Aviv]]]]
